    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Fuuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 7</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You release an ear-splitting blast of wind that deals 2d6 damage (half wind, half sonic; Fortitude halves). On a failed save, creatures are also deafened for 1d4+1 rounds. Exposed brittle or crystalline objects take 1d6 damage per level. Creatures holding them can make a Reflex save to negate the damage to the objects.</p>\n\n\n\n",
